{"article_id":"D3eO0LxFO5a3BEr4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Friday publicly urged Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell to deploy the so-called \" nuclear option \"","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"to jam through a controversial spending package","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that includes billions in border-wall funds ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"as Washington ' s warring parties remain on a collision course toward a partial government shutdown at midnight .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"\" Mitch , use the Nuclear Option","depth":12},{"id":5,"text":"and get it done !","depth":12},{"id":6,"text":"Our Country is counting on you ! \"","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"the president tweeted ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"referring to congressional slang","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"for overhauling the Senate filibuster","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"so legislation can pass with just 51 votes , as opposed to the usual 60 .","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"The president prodded McConnell to shatter Senate precedent","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"after the House approved $ 5.7 billion for a border wall as part of a measure","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"to fund the government through early February .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Trump hailed the 217-185 vote as a big victory","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"- one","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that GOP leaders scrambled to cobble together","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"when the president abruptly backed off tacit support for an earlier Senate-approved stopgap","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"that did not include the wall money .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"With a 60-vote threshold , however , the House-passed package stands little chance","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"of being endorsed on the Senate side .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Trump backed the \" nuclear option \"","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"after Sen. Steve Daines , R-Mont. , and others called for it .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"\" House just passed a bill","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that fully funds government","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and enables @ realDonaldTrump to secure our border/build the wall .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Senate can do same","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"by eliminating the filibuster .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"51 votes , same","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"as we do for judges ! \"","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Daines tweeted .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"who was meeting with Senate Republicans late Friday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"afterward said","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Daines has his `` total support '' in that effort .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"McConnell , however , repeatedly has said","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"he would not go this route on legislation .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"Such a drastic change would likely struggle to pick up enough support even among Senate Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"though the chamber has been steadily eroding filibuster precedent","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"to ease the path for the confirmation of presidential nominees","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"dating back to the Obama administration .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"A McConnell aide noted Friday","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that he `` has said for years","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that the votes are not there in the Conference","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"to use the nuclear option . ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Other senators seemed to back McConnell on that point .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Moments before Trump 's tweet , White House Press Secretary Sarah Sanders made clear on `` Fox & Friends ''","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"that the administration supported the nuclear option calls .","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"\" They should","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"[ lower the threshold ] .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"This is such an important issue","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"and it ' s something","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that all of America wants to see happen , ''","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"she said ,","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"calling for the Senate to do \" whatever is necessary","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"to get the job done . ''","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"The end-game remains unclear .","depth":2},{"id":57,"text":"Just two days ago , Trump seemed resigned to backing a stopgap spending package","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"without his sought-after wall money , for the sake","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"of avoiding a partial shutdown after Friday 's midnight deadline .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"But","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"after a backlash from conservatives","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"worried","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"the president 's wall promise would effectively crumble","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"once Democrats take the House next month ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Trump reversed course","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"to insist on the funding","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"-- resulting in Thursday 's House vote .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Yet Senate Democrats are in no mood to go along with the House Republican package .","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"`` The Trump temper tantrum may produce a government shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"It will not get him his wall , ''","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , said .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Absent a sudden compromise or an even more unlikely filibuster change ,","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"funding for nine of 15 Cabinet-level departments and dozens of agencies could lapse at midnight ,","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"resulting in a partial shutdown","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"just as the Christmas break begins .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Both sides were busy assigning blaming Friday morning , in anticipation of that scenario .","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"While Schumer and House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi have already branded this outcome a Trump shutdown ,","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"the president tweeted Friday","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that `` it will be a Democrat Shutdown ! ''","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"if they do n't support the measure before them in the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"`` No matter what happens today in the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Republican House Members should be very proud of themselves .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"They flew back to Washington from all parts of the World","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"in order to vote for Border Security and the Wall .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"Not one Democrat voted yes ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"and we won big .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"I am very proud of you ! ''","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"`` The Democrats ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"whose votes we need in the Senate ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"will probably vote against Border Security and the Wall","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"even though they know","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"it is DESPERATELY NEEDED .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"If the Dems vote no ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"there will be a shutdown","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"that will last for a very long time .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"People don ' t want Open Borders and Crime ! ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":153,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":143,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":128,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":118,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":116,"right":117,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":116,"left":101,"right":115,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":0,"right":99,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":1,"right